      <title>泰晤士水务转型计划或于今年加速启动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/thames-water-turnaround-regime-may-be-accelerated-to-start-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务公司的重整计划可能会在今年年底前受到监管机构的监督，因为该公司正竞相避开五月份的最后期限，因为届时它将耗尽资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/thames-water-turnaround-regime-may-be-accelerated-to-start-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:58:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士股市 13 个月内第二次停电，停市数小时</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/swiss-stock-exchange-trading-halted-due-to-technical-issues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士证券市场运营商周三因技术故障无法发布定价数据而暂停股票交易数小时，这是该交易所有史以来最长的宕机，也是一年多以来第二次宕机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/swiss-stock-exchange-trading-halted-due-to-technical-issues</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:13:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯接近结束持续四个季度的经济衰退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/saudi-economy-gdp-contracts-for-fourth-quarter-on-opec-oil-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着 OPEC+ 石油减产效应开始减弱，沙特阿拉伯经济萎缩速度有所放缓，但本季度开始可能出现好转，结束自一年前开始的连续下滑趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/saudi-economy-gdp-contracts-for-fourth-quarter-on-opec-oil-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 06:19:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行重启经济 日元飙升至 3 月以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/yen-drops-even-after-boj-lifts-policy-rate-as-yield-gaps-remain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本央行提高利率并宣布削减债券购买计划后，日元兑美元汇率飙升至3月份以来的最高水平，重新引发强劲上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/yen-drops-even-after-boj-lifts-policy-rate-as-yield-gaps-remain</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 04:12:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯领导人被杀再度引发地缘政治风险，油价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯称以色列杀死了其政治领导人，此举加剧了该地区（该地区原油产量占全球三分之一）的紧张局势，导致油价出现自四月份以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 23:29:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英伟达股价上涨 11%：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在受创芯片制造商股价上涨的推动下，股市出现反弹，而最新的经济数据增强了人们对美联储将在 9 月份降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 22:44:39 GMT</pubDate>
